title: Oven-Ready Cherry Dijon Glazed Pork Chops with Pillsbury™️ Buttermilk Southern Homestyle Biscuits & Roasted Green Beans (trays included)
description: Craving some down-home-style comfort? We reckon you’ve come to the right place! We’re serving up pork chops coated in a mix of Dijon mustard, cherry jam, and BBQ seasonings, flaky buttermilk biscuits sprinkled with cheddar cheese, and a side of roasted green beans. The best part, though? There’s minimal clean up! We send you trays so you get to spend more time digging in, and less time sudsing up. Dinner is served, ya’ll.
